title: ERA MSS output channels
agents: snmp
author: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH <info@kuhn-ruess.de>
license: GPL
distribution: none
description:
 Reads the outChannTable (OID .1.3.6.1.4.1.11588.1.5.105) and creates one
 service per output channel. Reports outChannState, outChannEnc1/Enc2 labels
 and emits perfdata for throughput (outChannBps) and total bytes sent
 (outChannBytes). Configurable upper and lower WARN/CRIT levels for the
 throughput are available via the {ERA output channels} ruleset.

perfdata:
 era_outchann_bps (B/s), era_outchann_bytes (total B)

item:
 "<index> <encoder label>" (outChannIndex + outChannEnc1).

inventory:
 One service per channel with a populated, non-"n/a" state.
